1
00:00:45,480 --> 00:00:46,760
Ayan has caught his royal brother

2
00:00:46,760 --> 00:00:49,400
staring blankly in the study several times.

3
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:52,360
But after Sister Xiaoyue came,

4
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:54,160
royal brother started smiling.

5
00:00:56,600 --> 00:01:00,000
Is he really that lonely?

6
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:04,400
If you are worried about him,

7
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:05,940
go and check on him.

8
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:09,440
He does seem a bit different today.

9
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:13,010
I'll go check on him.

10
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:14,720
Wait.

11
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:18,890
Are you really leaving?

12
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:22,600
Damn data man.

13
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:35,340
You want to drink, too.

14
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:41,120
I will satisfy you.

15
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,520
How is it?

16
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:50,720
Is it good?

17
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:57,440
No.

18
00:01:58,320 --> 00:01:59,400
Not good.

19
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,820
What's wrong with you?

20
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,170
Why are your eyes so red?

21
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,620
Why did you go to see Jingyuan?

22
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:25,360
Ah.

23
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:27,480
What?

24
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:32,040
Speak.

25
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:32,880
Let go.

26
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,640
I am a human being, not your pet cat or dog.

27
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:41,650
Why do you care who I went to see?

28
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:55,880
Si Xingxuan.

29
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,320
His eyes are red,

30
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,360
and he looks violent.

31
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:10,440
He must be sick.

32
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:16,120
I need to get a royal physician to take a look at him.

33
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:20,420
I have studied medicine for fifty years.

34
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:23,890
I have never seen a pulse like Your Majesty's before.

35
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:27,320
Your Majesty goes mad and turns on everyone,

36
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:30,120
but it doesn't seem like an illness.

37
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,120
What's wrong?

38
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,040
Get out.

39
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:44,480
Speak.

40
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,360
Let go of me.

41
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,010
It's not an illness.

42
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:59,280
It's poison.

43
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,360
Report.

44
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:05,400
Your Majesty, I intercepted the Grand Princess's carriage

45
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,760
that was transferring Consort Rong's sister.

46
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:08,360
I don't know what kind of torture she suffered.

47
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:10,760
Talking about witchcraft and black magic.

48
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,240
Could there be...

49
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:17,880
strange places in Aunt's mansion?

50
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:21,520
Like an isolated little house,

51
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:22,930
strange noises,

52
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:25,680
or a dungeon?

53
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,080
Oh, yes.

54
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:29,320
Yes.

55
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:31,760
Last time I saw a little rabbit,

56
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:33,440
and it hopped and hopped,

57
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,920
then suddenly disappeared.

58
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,250
Suddenly disappeared?

59
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,000
Then Aunt said

60
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,159
not to enter that hole,

61
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:41,560
because she said there's a monster inside.

62
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,159
Then do you remember

63
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:45,480
where that monster is?

64
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,520
Are you going?

65
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,200
Okay.
